      "title": "Epidemiology and disease burden of lateral epicondylitis in the USA: analysis of 85,318 patients",
      "abstract": "Background ::: National rates of lateral epicondylitis and surgical treatment are poorly defined. Disease burden of lateral epicondylitis (LE) continues to increase annually. Further study is necessary to optimize treatment algorithms to reduce associated health-care expenditures."
    }
